attributes.action: Provide funding and improve procedures for survivors with PTSD/CPTSD
attributes.additional_details: As a survivor of rape I have witnessed the flaws in the current system, where there is no clear procedure or cooperation between organisations. This has worsened my condition on many occasions and I do not want others to suffer like I have.
attributes.background: Provide funding and work to create more effective procedures between relevant Charities, NHS, Police, Social services and any other agency to ensure survivors of trauma receive the correct treatment and care including psychotherapy
